{
  "stem": "13483.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were there to clean up the place, clear up, and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- I-- I went in there with my field regiment, I think a day before it was actually-- day after the first British troops had got in there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, April.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think the end of April or May.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it must have been any time between April and May, 1945.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By truck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, with my-- with my company, field regiment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember going through a big gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could see a lot of smoke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could smell the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But we entered the place, it was just a shambles, people laying dead or half dead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember seeing some great big pits that had been dug by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I think just disbelief, actually-- hard to describe, Susie.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think we were the second.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We might've been the first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even know, Susie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll be quite honest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We might have been the first British troops in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when we were there, British troops were already in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we might've just been on the tail end, just behind them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, movements were very, very hard to distinguish in those days, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Too far back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know we went through some two big gates though.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I remember the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where, German?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think they'd already been held captive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we might've just been on the second line that went in there, the second body of British soldiers that went in there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do-- do remember, when they brought out Josef Kramer and Irma Grese, and the other lady wardens.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
